0.9.name: wordpress/bens-translator
0.9.description: Bens Translator is a plugin for Wordpress that generates translated pages using Google Translator. The pages are cached by your webserver and displayed as a normal webpage. This allows indexing by Google and other search engines to boost your traffic.
